r />\n不過係寵物店買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而且仲有分 全剷 3mm 6mm 9mm<br />\n好好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbbdcf05c4e2012a1b3ba8d3a7f5124b7ab35af6","tid":149704,"uid":27734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T07:45:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去豐澤呀個D, 買個日本有牌子既, 300左右已經OK. 唔好去乜野直銷中心個D百幾蚊雜嘜. 最主要個分別係舊電. 日本貨充電起碼玩幾年(當你2個禮拜剪一次). 雜嘜可能一年唔夠已經打柴, 叉幾耐都係剪得個5分鐘, 如果剪到一半無電就仆街. 其實最好係可以剪個時插住電線直接攞電, 但係我舊個把壞左之後再揾都揾唔翻.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我用開嗰個可以直接插濕電用，叉電後用30分鐘<br />\n<br />\n不過係寵物店買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而且仲有分 全剷 3mm 6mm 9mm<br />\n好好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係豐澤買果個都有分mm 剷？"},{"pid":"180fbd411452f25d0c84532801b049d8338ca275","tid":149704,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:40:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://detail.tmall.com/item.htm?id=531940770655&amp;ns=1&amp;abbucket=11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdetail.tmall.com%2Fitem.htm%3Fid%3D531940770655%26ns%3D1%26abbucket%3D11&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1V0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=f8445c0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://detail.tmall.com/item.htm?id=531940770655&amp;ns=1&amp;abbucket=11</a><br />\n<br />\n用緊"},{"pid":"26b2de35865fa33fadb275684014bdeef4defae8","tid":149704,"uid":24559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:42:46.000Z","msg":"要買剪喎清"},{"pid":"91c7edb2c9fabf584fc89d3dc635a0da150e00f5","tid":149704,"uid":99794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:46:41.000Z","msg":"係普通電器舖買 300幾蚊 幾抵用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}